00:30:46.080 --> 00:30:48.750
called a LevelDB database.

00:30:48.750 --> 00:30:51.900
So those of you who are closer
to computer science than I

00:30:51.900 --> 00:30:55.860
could say all the pros and
cons of a LevelDB database.

00:30:55.860 --> 00:30:57.990
