00:53:58.060 --> 00:54:01.660
some economic or commercial
counterparty risk, which is,

00:54:01.660 --> 00:54:05.470
in finance, you take
it all the time,

00:54:05.470 --> 00:54:08.380
then maybe I can do it
in less than 10 minutes.

00:54:08.380 --> 00:54:10.720
And in fact, even
Starbucks, when

00:54:10.720 --> 00:54:14.470
Starbucks accepts your
credit card swipe,

00:54:14.470 --> 00:54:17.170
