bit of counterparty risk

00:54:17.170 --> 00:54:21.010
from the payment processing
company First Data.

00:54:21.010 --> 00:54:24.010
I don't mean to say that
it might not be also

00:54:24.010 --> 00:54:25.450
from Visa and the banks.

00:54:25.450 --> 00:54:28.210
But I'll just say
the payment system

00:54:28.210 --> 00:54:30.490
has some counterparty risk.

00:54:30.490 --> 00:54:32.890
Because final settlement
in our payment

00:54:32.890 --> 00:54:36.420
system doesn't happen
within seconds.

00:54:36.420 --> 00:54:39.210
So the actual answer--
