00:57:38.610 --> 00:57:46.710
The essence of mining is
creating an incentive structure

00:57:46.710 --> 00:57:50.520
where there is no
central authority

00:57:50.520 --> 00:57:56.850
to validate and put a new
set of transactions or data--

00:57:56.850 --> 00:57:59.310
I'm going to say broadly, data--

00:57:59.310 --> 00:58:06.050
into the ledger, into the
accepted state of what

00:58:06.050 --> 00:58:08.480
reality is.

00:58:08.480 --> 00:58:10.010
So mining helps with that.

00:58:10.010 --> 00:58:12.030
That's that whole process.

00:58:12.030 --> 00:58:15.770
In essence, who gets to
decide the next block of data?

00:58:15.770 --> 00:58:21.430
Transactions are included in the
data, but it's not identical.

00:58:21.430 --> 00:58:27.880
Mining is really critical, but
