it, is there a condition?

00:58:49.570 --> 00:58:52.030
Might there even be this
little bit of scripting code

00:58:52.030 --> 00:58:53.830
that puts other
conditions, like there

00:58:53.830 --> 00:58:57.150
has to be multiple signatures?

00:58:57.150 --> 00:58:58.275
Has it been double spent?

00:59:01.810 --> 00:59:04.230
